I made these toy 2D games to play around with the nice Lua 2D game framework:

https://love2d.org/

Escape from Earth is a shooter in the style of Guxt by Pixel(cave story creator)

Tower defense is self-describing.

Collect the Dots is a dexterity game where dots materialize in random locations
and there are also random obstacles. The dots always move toward your pointer,
so you have to place it to bring the dots together as quickly as possible.
